This set of data was collected to confirm sav maps created using biobase. The first map was created by moving parrallel to shore; turning around and mapping 5 m farther from shore; turning around; again 5m away from the preceding run. In total 4 parrallel lines were mapped. (named Sonar test 1 in the lowerance; mapping began around 08:48). The samples associated with Sonar Test 1 are SAV extras2-5. Another sampling design was tested: it consisted of 3 parralel lines run parralel to shore each spread apart by aprox. 10m. Sampling began at aprox. 09:03. SAV extras6-10 were associated with the second sampling design.
